Pre-Game Insights: The final match of the T20 World Cup will be played between Pakistan and England on Sunday, November 13, 2022.
Pakistan and England have a history of head-to-head encounters with England holding an edge over Pakistan in past T20 World Cup meetings.
Babar Azam and Jos Buttler are key players expected to play crucial roles in the match.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match has rekindled memories of the 1992 ODI World Cup final between the two countries.
The unpredictable nature of the T20 format gives both teams equal chances to reclaim the glory.
